  "content": "<p><span>25年开年以来，业界对于AI Agent的讨论尤其多，我自己的播客也是；</span></p><span></span>\n<p><span>从Deepseek爆火那期节目到上期manus，都是围绕Agent展开的；</span></p><span></span>\n<p><span>近期有朋友找我希望给他的同事说说Agent这个话题，所以有了今天这期播客。</span></p><span></span>\n<p><span>这期内容中有大概1/3的内容其实来自于之前Manus那期节目，</span></p><span></span>\n<p><span>那些内容的详细部分如果大家有兴趣可以去听我之前的播客：</span><a href=\"https://www.xiaoyuzhoufm.com/episode/67d244bbe924d4525a3e15a7\" data-url=\"https://www.xiaoyuzhoufm.com/episode/67d244bbe924d4525a3e15a7\"><span>manus没有秘密</span></a><span>。</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/Fh9hr4yL0B4jPFU-peZFOFjB6NUV.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span>PPT可以到我的ima知识库获取：</span></p><span></span>\n<p><span>链接：<a data-url=\"https://wiki.ima.qq.com/knowledge-base-share?shareId=28a804fef7bbb90209159f2e78690d683a27081e87bf4c2597420c0fa117f0ad\" href=\"https://wiki.ima.qq.com/knowledge-base-share?shareId=28a804fef7bbb90209159f2e78690d683a27081e87bf4c2597420c0fa117f0ad\">wiki.ima.qq.com</a></span></p><span></span>\n<p><span>或者扫这个二维码：</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FqvFMiJ1npCx8sJBgabloDkQNpfY.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span>欢迎把这个播客或者文件转发给任何你觉得值得分享的地方。</span></p><span></span>\n<p><span>以及时隔半个月又是一期几十页的PPT solo节目……</span></p><span></span>\n<p><span>我真的有点肝不动了……😭</span></p><span></span>\n<p><em><span>（想加粉丝群的请先+微信：rosicky311)</span></em></p><span></span>\n<p><span>下面正片开始……</span></p><span></span>\n<p><strong><span>【时间线】</span></strong></p><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"72\">01:12</a> 一个关于群响的小故事</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FjWIoDZDeG4jFdGb10-OoycsewSY.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"178\">02:58</a> 意外的报名人数</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FqRrMNRdsG0YAVrRI-Ulppsj6aQF.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"312\">05:12</a> 智谱发布AutoGLM沉思版</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/Fi-M94a4j7P-chK6QdsUlh4q-idG.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"409\">06:49</a> 目录页</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FkGPUzwWVnzXPVnu6R3FtTdehzCG.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"415\">06:55</a> 老生常谈的L1-L5</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/Fqnv9hvHLLy_VA2CRNhRWyZBDe5s.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"507\">08:27</a> 我们是怎么走到的L1</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FqUKPDCkO_fXsJieNsCMKaNIAj6s.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"540\">09:00</a> 我们获得了“通用”大模型</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/Fva1wcHmrPksvVeUAtOpQkQCPdRB.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"582\">09:42</a> 我们是怎么走到的L2</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FiZZ4ZbKlNv2K1rK_SZDfJpPOzFE.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FrwrQwo_e_rYVAwGYbrccl34Xoc6.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FoIcLhGffuq_G6hIstAdChD9jrid.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/Fpvcr2TiUhOpCzZH7tuE01G8Mqb2.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"753\">12:33</a> 那些“共识”</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FibtLHgGjXN1InoGhklJaxq0Gf9Z.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"827\">13:47</a> 模型还是产品？</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/Fi8vFTLFjJ-tsWboP4ajvlIz2arb.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"846\">14:06</a> 基于Capex的粗暴逻辑</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FqJopKExqsuoQBMDSZGaGqHJI8MH.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"876\">14:36</a> 同一种叙事的不断重复</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FijrLt4NYKVUJskCkUSUxx_EBOVX.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"966\">16:06</a> 那产品的叙事呢？</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FspuUpyi5nnygO_csBlyq9AWFqVe.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"1010\">16:50</a> 用户需要“看见”</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FnMf0NUicMb8XNNQlfH2_1j3aWVi.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"1053\">17:33</a> manus定义的“看见”</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FoNisaZdQmcJglf-RLOzQvd0L1hJ.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"1145\">19:05</a> 从技术demo到产品</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FuDcbC8HgTRxatlWS5mEsXSVBWXw.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"1171\">19:31</a> et30榜单</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FrXqLe4KGKSPBYDqw3mzVGmYwC43.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"1331\">22:11</a> 投资人懂个P</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FlkHrxNZgCmmTznJo0Z9oetErR4D.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"1376\">22:56</a> Agent似乎不是产品</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FiKh5_53DRVmupFAAn5wor5G7Okg.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"1412\">23:32</a> 我们进入盲人摸象的阶段</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FnyXH_kg8DqRaX60roYHBXAa1bfW.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"1449\">24:09</a> 机核谈游戏与AI</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FhoQItAoZ7zz8lUn--1K4AMCI3Vf.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"1527\">25:27</a> 空对空谈</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/Fkg9SMpfN-HSfpYN4n0lg_zhOV2S.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"1543\">25:43</a> 去年和koji做的YC-AI项目统计</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FvG53Pp8yKXDa16_v6OgwjHV3JQ9.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"1618\">26:58</a> 我们也看到过很多这种</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FiRhQEAicnZ3EqDOZAuE4uK0nPl1.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"1630\">27:10</a> workflow“花活”</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FpvQbM7S4rJq3UBVXgIRsKfZ105j.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FohNVPZVSAxD_XrxAYSc3mGvkjp6.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"1666\">27:46</a> 那些“弯路”</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FmRkg5LM181PeC9gHKXyLf-6n-35.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"1755\">29:15</a> agent的演化</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FvtmTqZgvmzl2JrJdQxX9TPuMYJS.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"1770\">29:30</a> 收敛中的共识</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/Fv2JoSq674ZAkxsrclNtD6uTshLx.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"1885\">31:25</a> 继续基于特征的描述</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FuioVaGreSpNyw4LZ8bPIidTmfYq.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"2041\">34:01</a> 再一次模型即产品</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/Fj2j-BG46uohFXdtFBGcCb6cWUFx.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"2050\">34:10</a> deep……</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FhXJxfZbgTtSrql7ASNuow69tz3U.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"2105\">35:05</a> 正在发生的事情</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FmAUqXSvHOaM3st6Zga6bH56bU2X.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"2168\">36:08</a> 大家伙们都会做的</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/Ft6GK9eb4Ty9-x08c9_VoL0f6hG6.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"2224\">37:04</a> 模型即产品again</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FpTRDyB-Sob_GCpGcvh-Z08FFrpR.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"2291\">38:11</a> 早期投资集中在专业agent</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/Fqr17eD3r2OAyZJlj1JrfSXM7pZB.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"2313\">38:33</a> 垂直行业agent还处于早期</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FiY16v-AR3cO0-rwr13Bg_lgN77a.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"2350\">39:10</a> 基建不完善</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FrSX4eXS61DGmAmdXn7JOJ1QeyuU.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"2419\">40:19</a> 所有人都不会放弃成为平台的可能性</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FoaCfRRf0IAwIa6PIzPiu30nkou5.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"2436\">40:36</a> 关于mcp</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/Fhz335cPTmYc4KhygYte261roZr6.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FpVhZ-mEaedkGp5G3YDlsNkT8EFl.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"2468\">41:08</a> 享受到红利的初创公司</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FvxaSdJCRUHeiQdqH_2KT4dfvX1i.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"2517\">41:57</a> a1base的案例</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FrXV5bfe1Ca2uUE2EEK9p1-g9F6F.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"2592\">43:12</a> 暴论环节</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FtP5HXIJkNd8ahz12nHQjFHIBI8W.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"2601\">43:21</a> 通过边界定义</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FnNqbUceSqlKUyMTTabyDmQXNpRd.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"2636\">43:56</a> 怎么还有metaverse的事儿呢？</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FiScEyESUf4nkVxDDjxgUZ74IR_6.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"2650\">44:10</a> 传说中的微信Agent</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/Fo9fSRuIddBY8wPWNSWe3O7nOvcg.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"2776\">46:16</a> 黑猫白猫</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FtGvUmW8WTxEyjqNudw4jg3kB5p0.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FnrJmfXb7KY0IzJ1lpHvPAL_5jFt.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"2863\">47:43</a> 谈钱的话就不能不提定价了</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FjC076d-kULi_XwjTwxvojR3zLCy.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FrIbK_0mNmKNAi4XlEN4D8YkXVTp.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"3010\">50:10</a> epoch的观点</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/Fk1BC8phj2UMmihIX41hc5NX_rzW.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"3083\">51:23</a> 回到现实</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FvDaPamm3Tjax0s0u5IIoNGGNpyk.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FoUrKHrRAKeh3y6a0kK2cueA4c7S.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span>再次说下，PPT可以下载：</span></p><span></span>\n<p><span>链接：</span><a href=\"https://wiki.ima.qq.com/knowledge-base-share?shareId=28a804fef7bbb90209159f2e78690d683a27081e87bf4c2597420c0fa117f0ad\" data-url=\"https://wiki.ima.qq.com/knowledge-base-share?shareId=28a804fef7bbb90209159f2e78690d683a27081e87bf4c2597420c0fa117f0ad\"><span>wiki.ima.qq.com</span></a></p><span></span>\n<p><span>或者扫这个二维码：</span></p><span></span>\n<figure>\n <img src=\"https://image.xyzcdn.net/FqvFMiJ1npCx8sJBgabloDkQNpfY.png\">\n</figure><span></span>\n<p><span>音乐：AI音乐工具</span><a href=\"https://www.tianpuyue.cn/\" data-url=\"https://www.tianpuyue.cn/\"><span>天谱乐</span></a><span>生成</span></p><span></span>\n<p><span>【播客简介】</span></p><span></span>\n<p><span>屠龙之术是一档关注科技、互联网、风险投资的播客，</span></p><span></span>\n<p><span>主播庄明浩是一个游走在互联网和风险投资行业的边缘人士。</span></p><span></span>\n<p><span>其工作多年所积累的认知似乎都成为了某种意义上的”屠龙之术“……</span></p><span></span>\n<p><span>或许某天再有新的“龙”出现的时候，就是这档播客停更之时。</span></p>",
  "aiSummary": "本期播客深入探讨了 AI Agent 的定义、发展阶段、行业现状、技术挑战与未来趋势，并分享了对产品叙事、商业模式和投资策略的思考。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本期播客深入探讨了 AI Agent 的定义、发展阶段、行业现状、技术挑战与未来趋势，并分享了对产品叙事、商业模式和投资策略的思考。",
  "summary": "本期播客由庄明浩主讲，深入探讨了 AI Agent 领域的热点话题。首先，回顾了 AI 从 L1 到 L5 的发展阶段，强调了通用大模型的重要性。接着，讨论了模型与产品的关系，指出智能创新在 AI 时代的重要性，以及用户对“看见”AI Agent 规划和执行过程的需求。通过分析行业报告，揭示了 AI native 公司比例的提升和产品趋势的变化。随后，用“盲人摸象”的比喻生动地描述了当前行业对 Agent 理解的碎片化和共识的缺乏。并对 Agent 的四个特征：记忆、规划能力、工具调用和行为记忆进行了总结。最后，探讨了 AI Agent 的开发工具、平台、商业模式、定价策略以及面临的推理成本、用户信任等挑战。整体而言，本期播客内容丰富，涵盖了 AI Agent 领域的多个维度，既有对技术发展的回顾与展望，也有对产品和商业模式的深入思考，为听众提供了全面的视角。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI Agent 的定义和理解在行业内存在碎片化和不一致",
      "explanation": "如同盲人摸象，不同的人对 AI Agent 的理解侧重于不同的特征，缺乏整体共识，导致产品和技术边界模糊不清。"
    },
    {
      "point": "用户对 AI Agent 产品的“看见”需求，要求产品展现规划、执行和交付的完整过程",
      "explanation": "用户希望看到 AI Agent 如何规划任务、逐步执行，并最终交付成果，从而感受到 AI 的智能和价值。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI Agent 的价值主要来源于自动化，而非研发本身",
      "explanation": "专注于自动化普通工作任务的 AI Agent，例如浏览互联网、操作商业软件等，可能更有利可图。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "我对用盲人摸象来形容当下这个行业的状态。",
    "也是只不过是因为这一代的所谓大语言模型代表的 AI 在游戏行业并没有得到特别好的应用的展现。",
    "我们怀疑在可见的未来，人工智能实验室专注于尝试自动化普通工作任务将有利可图。",
    "但实际情况并不是这样，推理成本依然很高，复杂的环境真的还是不行，用户不信任，交互体验依然有创新的地方。",
    "第一，MA 是 CSIG 做的，微信怎么可能让一个 CSIG 的产品成为自己的中枢呢？"
  ],
